title: Marvel - The End (collected) (- Nem -)
description:
The End is a line of comic books published by Marvel Comics. They follow possible endings for various Marvel characters, as they are set in the future.


    Iron Man: The End (one shot)

    Incredible Hulk: The End (one shot)

    She-Hulk: The End (She-Hulk #12)

    The Punisher: The End (one shot)

    X-Men: The End (a trilogy of miniseries, 18 issues in all)

    Wolverine: The End (6 issues limited series)

    Marvel: The End, also published as Thanos: The End (6 issues limited series)

    Fantastic Four: The End (6 issues limited series)
